@startuml Infyro_User_Experience_Flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName SansSerif
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #EEF2FF
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #4F46E5
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #64748B
skinparam ArrowColor #334155
skinparam TitleFontSize 16
skinparam TitleFontColor #0F172A

title Infyro — User experience flow\nBeta 0.0.1 · create agents · connect channels · use tools

|You|
start
:Open Infyro dashboard\n(beta 0.0.1);

|Dashboard|
:Land on Home — see your agents\nat a glance (status, last activity);

:Create a new agent\n(any purpose you want — not locked to finance);

partition "Customise the agent" {
  :Name + avatar color;
  :Persona / how it should talk;
  :Model settings\n(provider, temperature, style);
  :Paste your own LLM API key (BYOK);
  :Attach tools / MCPs\n(live data, actions, your APIs…);
  :Pick channels to reach people\n(Telegram · Slack · Email · more…);
}

:Save — agent is ready;

|Channels|
:Link a channel from Settings\ne.g. Telegram / Slack / Email;

fork
  :Message the agent\non that channel;
fork again
  :Agent can pull **live data**\nvia tools (quotes, docs, APIs…);
fork again
  :Or run an **action** via MCP\ne.g. user says "buy Sensex"\non Telegram → trading MCP executes\n(example of tool-driven actions);
end fork

|Dashboard|
:Review replies, memory, alerts;
:Tweak temperature, persona,\ntools, or channels anytime;
:Pause / resume / delete agents;

note right
  **Beta 0.0.1**
  Finance niche in this build
  is a demo — the product idea is
  “your agents, your channels,
  your tools.”
end note

stop

legend right
  |= Idea |= Meaning |
  | Agent | A customisable AI worker you create |
  | Channel | Where you talk to it (Tele, Slack, Email…) |
  | Tool / MCP | Live data **or** real actions |
  | BYOK | Your LLM key — you control cost |
endlegend

@enduml
